{"tid":848380,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A]Dragalia Lost ～失落的龍絆～ 請跟返自己戰力入場（14）","createTime":"2018-10-05T01:12:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T05:08:02.000Z","uid":3508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"463c4735b47a2152dc594d1a8f8521f7ce923c08","tid":848380,"uid":3508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T01:12:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[I/A]Dragalia Lost ～失落的龍絆～ 忠龍祈願故王的靈魂葬禮（10）<br />\n<br />\n任天堂與 Cygames 攜手打造的arpg <br />\n<br />\n角色能透過「龍化」，化身為與其締結契約的龍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/03/140701_72ff37b86353e5a812ff1ede8b67764e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F03%2F140701_72ff37b86353e5a812ff1ede8b67764e.png&h=ef001d0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/03/140711_b249210ec5ddc893f15f5f3ef662da69.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F03%2F140711_b249210ec5ddc893f15f5f3ef662da69.png&h=1bc5b2a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/03/140720_4f87d25f9d6256f4a84497db6bdba564.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F03%2F140720_4f87d25f9d6256f4a84497db6bdba564.png&h=51271aec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/03/140733_f989b1cb06829f08f08f34d075e26037.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F03%2F140733_f989b1cb06829f08f08f34d075e26037.png&h=f54c71dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/03/140742_275df6919db76ae6dbc8fd40a04b5db6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F03%2F140742_275df6919db76ae6dbc8fd40a04b5db6.png&h=8c4902ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/03/140809_bbfda0799f1d03d2d9daa8444a46dea0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F03%2F140809_bbfda0799f1d03d2d9daa8444a46dea0.png&h=2de2d11b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/03/140820_11e7eb6d5c92850eb36fb3068c94272f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F03%2F140820_11e7eb6d5c92850eb36fb3068c94272f.png&h=fed5f542&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/03/140830_b53edcf3d3cf3d56e68d742dab4d3fde.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F03%2F140830_b53edcf3d3cf3d56e68d742dab4d3fde.png&h=4f88a65b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/03/140840_9555427561d87ceab84424e5d29a05cf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F03%2F140840_9555427561d87ceab84424e5d29a05cf.png&h=39be2ead&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/03/142308_18aa73b4321ca80dd5d02302215d6f4d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F03%2F142308_18aa73b4321ca80dd5d02302215d6f4d.png&h=232478d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n4/10 更新<br />\n團隊遊戲模式下挑戰火屬性的團體戰 BOSS<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=RKA40l2zGTg&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRKA40l2zGTg%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=hHJgFXFQMACfCY1nZCs3oNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=6866375a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=RKA40l2zGTg&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n首抽:<br />\n一角一龍可以開，最好同屬性<br />\n<br />\n評價網:<br />\n<a href=\"https://game8.jp/dragalialost/233911\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgame8.jp%2Fdragalialost%2F233911&d=hHJgFXFQMACfCY1nZCs3oNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=72ea8cde\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://game8.jp/dragalialost/233911</a><br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A:<br />\n刷幾隻角，龍先開得？<br />\n你有一角一龍都可以開，有人刷幾日都未有<br />\n<br />\n要做啲乜？<br />\n打主線，副本<br />\n<br />\n同人合作打有幾多石？<br />\n50石一個人，最多2500石<br />\n<br />\n點升戰力？<br />\n升lvl<br />\n升環<br />\n龍<br />\n造武<br />\n建築<br />\n卡<br />\n<br />\n點有多啲瑪那？<br />\n打主線，錢關<br />\n課金<br />\n<br />\n點造高星武？<br />\n升建築lvl再升主城同鍛造<br />\n<br />\n唔夠錢點算？<br />\n打錢關<br />\n<br />\n資源唔夠？<br />\n諗定:<br />\n升咩角色先<br />\n武器玩3星3段屬性定4星2段<br />\n<br />\n爆發攻擊(蓄力)可以破盾，也可以大幅減少OD(技能槽)<br />\n<br />\n紅色預警圈可以使用技能無敵幀擋住，紫色的不行<br />\n昏迷&mdash;&mdash;受到攻擊後方可解除<br />\n黑暗&mdash;&mdash;命中率下降<br />\n濕身&mdash;&mdash;必被暴擊<br />\n冰凍&mdash;&mdash;被同伴攻擊後可解除</blockquote>"},{"pid":"65e33ef1d11ec50242b3fc0ec12d4f7bf78aa0ec","tid":848380,"uid":42340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T01:13:42.000Z","msg":"點解大家成日1001都唔開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77455b2a037df42cda50672b5cbc35f09551f317","tid":848380,"uid":21873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T01:14:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 留名"},{"pid":"cc4fbe52f49c9f3e41ec106b7c881f46b7db3880","tid":848380,"uid":3508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T01:14:58.000Z","msg":"過隔離啦"},{"pid":"c8a0a5cfee15527290f490ebce72c1fa6ebf98f1","tid":848380,"uid":142166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T04:32:04.000Z","msg":"小弟中左莉莉同五星暗龍同一個五星護符 開唔開波好"},{"pid":"115c545492d27b8ad71c521d8ec1f3f13ec50636","tid":848380,"uid":58275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T05:08:02.000Z","msg":"想問異界的碎片有咩用"}]}